Introduction

12DAL is a one-member South Korean band formed by XX Entertainment. The band debuted with two members: Nayul and Yerim on August 8, 2018 with digital single, "A Second". On September 1, 2020, Yerim announced her departure from 12DAL, making 12DAL a one-member band.
